dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Gilroy Hot Springs quadrangle, Santa Clara County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Gilroy Hot Springs, CA, 1955. Photorevised 1971. Photoinspected 1978. DMA 1758 III SW - Series V895." "Jon Kuespert honorary map." "First printing, July 2007." Includes location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology, most recent 1972. Includes "pertinent references", most recent 1999.
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
